snippet.title: This is GOALS
snippet.description:
Step into the future of football gaming, where gameplay meets fun and responsiveness. Join our playtest to be a part of GOALS' development and contribute to shaping our tribute to everything football.

PC gamers, add GOALS to your wishlist or request playtest access on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2753000/GOALS/

Follow us on socials 📱
https://instagram.com/goalsfreetoplay 
https://twitter.com/PlayGOALS 
https://www.tiktok.com/@playgoals 
https://discord.gg/goals

Stay updated via our website 🌐
https://playgoals.com/ 

#PlayGOALS #EveryonesGame
